<p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">为大力弘扬爱国主义精神，培育和践行社会主义核心价值观，教育师生勿忘国耻、奋发图强，9月18日上午7时，我校庄严举行纪念“九一八”事变发生日升国旗仪式。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">我院统筹安排新生营、连庄严列队，共同见证这一庄重的时刻。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240919/1726747130812072317.png" title="1726747130812072317.png" alt="b2ab4b7c6cd560b1331f640cda871ef.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">开场前</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">全体师生一起唱响《歌唱祖国》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">深情悠扬的歌声唱响校园 祝愿伟大祖国繁荣昌盛</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">国旗护卫队迈着铿锵有力的步伐</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">将五星红旗护送至升旗台</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">“升国旗，奏唱国歌！”</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">雄壮的《义勇军进行曲》奏响 五星红旗缓缓升起</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">全场肃立，行注目礼</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">师生们在凝重的氛围里</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">追思历史，祭奠英烈</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240919/1726747150882062818.png" title="1726747150882062818.png" alt="8efa21f075555952e2bac5deff62580.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">回顾历史 缅怀先辈</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">激情昂扬 字字铿锵</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240919/1726747176002039445.png" title="1726747176002039445.png" alt="e91ed886d08ab92debec6270f86a41a.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">仪式最后</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">全体师生齐唱《先锋之歌》</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">响彻云霄的是誓言</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">是师生们的坚定信念和决心</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">1931 9 · 18</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">血与泪</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">不曾忘 不敢忘 不能忘</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">心中长鸣警钟声</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">铭记历史，缅怀先烈，吾辈自强！</span></p><p><br/></p>